@startuml
title decisions-demo: pick one when you can't decide

|Session Agent|
start

:**Ask**: "What are you choosing between?
List 2 to 5 options, one per line."; <<output>>

|User|
:Provide options;

|Session Agent|
:**Input**:
  ↳ options
; <<input>>

if (only one option provided?) then (yes)
  :**Inform**: "Looks like you only gave me one option.
  The decision is already made."; <<output>>
else (no)
  :**Cue**: [[weigh-options.puml weigh-options]] with options
    ↳ chosen-option,
    ↳ reasoning
  ; <<procedure>>

  :**Inform**: "I'd go with: {chosen-option}.
  ({reasoning})"; <<output>>
endif

stop
@enduml
